page.title: 05HIGH STREET,WELLINGTON
page.content: This sreet is lined mainly with shops and small businesses.There are :_ 3 Firms of Solicitors, a Vetinary Practice,1 Firm of Accountants, a Conservative Club, the Main Post Office, a Job Centre, 2 Estate Agents, 2 Public Houses, 2 Restaurants, a Chinese Takeaway & a Fish & Chip Shop, & 2 Servicing Garages. The shops include:- 1 Chemist, 2 Greengrocers, a Petshop, 2 Bakers, 2 Butchers, a Shoe Shop, 2 Clothes Shops, 2 Toy/cycle Shops, a Garden Centre, a Hairdresser's/Video Shop, a Dry Cleaner's, a Craft Shop, a Furniture Shop, a Newsagents,a Super- market, an Electrical Shop, & a Sport shop. Wellington has it's own Newspaper, {"The Wellington Weekly"}whose offices can be found in this street. There is also a{Pedestrian Crossing.
